pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Grape Seed 14250mg 300 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Grape Seed Body & Beauty is a premium quality formula to support collagen formation, skin health & antioxidant activity, as well as helping to provide symptomatic relief associated with mild varicose veins.

Swisse Ultiboost Grape Seed Body & Beauty is a premium quality formula to support collagen formation, skin health & antioxidant activity, as well as helping to provide symptomatic relief associated with mild varicose veins.

Vitamin C maintains the health and formation of collagen to support healthy bright skin. Collagen is a major protein found in connective tissues, an important component of the skin's matrix. 

Vitamin C helps the formation of connective tissue and supports the healing process of minor wounds.

Grape seed and vitamin C provide antioxidant support to help reduce free radical damage to body cells and maintain general health and wellbeing.

Grape seeds contain high levels of procyanidins which are naturally occurring bioflavonoids that are also found in fruits and vegetables.

Grape seed helps reduce and relieve symptoms associated with mild varicose veins such as leg swelling, pain, aching, heaviness and itchy legs.

Suitable For: Vegetarians.

Lifestyle Claim: Vegetarian

Size: 300 Pack

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.  Do not use if cap seal is broken.

Ingredients

Grape seed (Vitis vinifera extract 118.75mg) equiv. dry seed (standardised to contain procyanidins 95mg) 14.25g and Vitamin C (ascorbic acid from calcium ascorbate dihydrate) 22.5mg.

Contains: Contains Sulfites.

Allergen Free From: Artificial Flavours| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Soy| Yeast

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:
Two tablets daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.

Storage Temperature: 25 degrees Celsius

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Swisse is a carbon neutral company. Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
